<div class="login_box">
    <div class="main_blocks">
        <img src="../img/login.jpg">
    </div>
    <div class="main_blocks">
        <div class="login_text_container">
            <p class="login_text">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque ultricies nunc vitae posuere dapibus. Nam sed orci vitae velit condimentum ultrices et a ante. Quisque non convallis sapien, eu vestibulum orci. Pellentesque euismod malesuada porta. Donec odio lorem, vestibulum sit amet felis vitae, hendrerit tristique massa. Nunc ultrices porta ligula nec blandit. Ut nec quam lacus. Nunc porttitor lacus non magna laoreet, eu semper sapien volutpat.                 
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main_blocks">
        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <div class="form_flex">
                <label for="login">Login</label>
                <input type="text" name="login" id="login">
                <label for="pass">Password</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="pass">
                {{#if incorrect}}
                    <p>username or password is incorrect</p>
                {{/if}}
                <input id="submit_button" type="submit" name="submit" value="Log In">
            </div>
        </form>
        <p>Haven't created account yet? <a href="../signup">Sign Up</a></p>
    </div>
</div>